  FAQ + FOOTER + STICKY + TABS (v14.2.1) — DROP-IN (PREMIUM UNITY PASS)

  Preserves:
  - #faq + #faqTitle + [data-ff-faq] + [data-ff-faq-item]
  - Share / Trust triggers: [data-ff-share-open], [data-ff-policy-open], [data-ff-proof-open], [data-ff-copy-link]
  - Footer IDs: #footerOrgName #footerOrgMeta #ffYear + [data-ff-powered]
  - Sticky IDs: #stickyRaised #stickyGoal #stickyGift #stickyTeam #stickyImpact
  - Tabs: [data-ff-tabs] + [data-ff-tab]
  - Back to top: [data-ff-backtotop] (NO [hidden] attribute)

